::Shadow Wing/Spears::

Shadow Wing::
She yells,"YES!" as the screen stays on.  She crawls back under the 
console and starts to fix some of the memory boards.  This was going 
to be a long day.  Now that it had power, she would have to restore 
it's voice box and 'brain'.  And that was only if it was possable.  
The comp was blown to bits.  She would have to get a new screen for 
Teletran when she could.

Spear::
She looked at Rodimus," I need to get to those cannons up there and 
repair them, can you give me a hand up there?"
